sec.p:
The present study is based on specimens deposited in the collections of the
Museum Zoologicum Bogoriense (MZB), Cibinong, Indonesia;
Natural History Collection at Ibaraki University (IUNH), Mito, Japan;
National Museum of Nature and Science (NMST), Tsukuba, Japan and the
Institute of Ecology and Biological Resources (IEBR), Hanoi, Vietnam.
